<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta viewport="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Character Selection</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/custom/BcharStyles.css">

<div class="carousel">
    <!-- list item -->
    <div class="list">
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/image/Custom/WarriorGirl.jpg">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="author">STORMBREAKER</div>
                <div class="title">BRYNHILDR</div>
                <div class="topic">BJORN</div>
                <div class="des">
                    Fierce as the storms of legend, Brynhildr lives up to her namesake,<br>
                    a Valkyrie reborn.  Her weapon, "Stormbreaker," <br>
                    is as much an extension of her will as it is forged steel.
                </div>
                <div class="buttons">
                    <a href='BasicLobby.html'>SELECT</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/image/Custom/WarriorBoy.jpg">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="author">IRONFIST</div>
                <div class="title">AETHELRED</div>
                <div class="topic">VANCE</div>
                <div class="des">
                    His name carries the weight of noble lineage,<br>
                    but his reputation as "Ironfist" speaks louder.<br>
                    Every battle-scarred knuckle tells a tale of unwavering strength.
                </div>
                <div class="buttons">
                    <a href='BasicLobby.html'>SELECT</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/image/Custom/MageGirl.jpg">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="author">STARLIGHT</div>
                <div class="title">SERAPHINA</div>
                <div class="topic">MOONBEAM</div>
                <div class="des">
                    Don't be fooled by the ethereal beauty of her name.<br>
                    Seraphina, like the "Starlight" she commands,<br>
                    holds immense magical power within.
                </div>
                <div class="buttons">
                    <a href='BasicLobby.html'>SELECT</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/image/Custom/MageBoy.jpg">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="author">SHADOWBINDER</div>
                <div class="title">CORVUS</div>
                <div class="topic">ESCHER</div>
                <div class="des">
                    With eyes like obsidian and movements<br>
                    as silent as a raven's wing, Corvus is shrouded in mystery.<br>
                    Those who dare to underestimate him soon learn the true meaning of "Shadowbinder."
                </div>
                <div class="buttons">
                    <a href='BasicLobby.html'>SELECT</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/image/Custom/RangerGirl.jpg">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="author">WHISPHERWIND</div>
                <div class="title">ELARA</div>
                <div class="topic">NIGHTSHADE</div>
                <div class="des">
                    Like a phantom breeze, Elara, named for a graceful nymph,<br>
                    moves unseen through the wilds.  Her connection to nature,<br>
                    symbolized by "Nightshade," makes her a master of stealth and survival.
                </div>
                <div class="buttons">
                    <a href='BasicLobby.html'>SELECT</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/image/Custom/RangerBoy.jpg">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="author">SWIFTARROW</div>
                <div class="title">HAWKEYE</div>
                <div class="topic">TALON</div>
                <div class="des">
                    His vision is as sharp as the hawk's he's named after,<br>
                    and his arrows fly with the speed of the "Swiftarrow."<br>
                    Hawkeye's unmatched skill makes him a legend on the battlefield.
                </div>
                <div class="buttons">
                    <a href='BasicLobby.html'>SELECT</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Popup Form Modal -->
        <div id="formModal" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close">&times;</span>
                <form id="userInfoForm">
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <label for="name">Name:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <label for="username">Username:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="username" name="username">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <label for="studentID">Student ID:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="studentID" name="studentID">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <label for="section">Section:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="section" name="section">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- list thumnail -->
    <div class="thumbnail">
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/image/Custom/WarriorGirl.jpg">
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/image/Custom/WarriorBoy.jpg">
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/image/Custom/MageGirl.jpg">
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/image/Custom/MageBoy.jpg">
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/image/Custom/RangerGirl.jpg">
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/image/Custom/RangerBoy.jpg">
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- next prev -->

    <div class="arrows">
        <button id="prev"><</button>
        <button id="next">></button>
    </div>
    <!-- time running -->
    <div class="time"></div>
</div>
<script src="~/js/custom/BcharScript.js"></script>